<view class="page skills-page theme-toolbox">
  <view class="page-head floral-title-box title-pattern-card"><image class="title-pattern-image" src="/assets/title-patterns/deep-purple.png" mode="aspectFill" /><view class="title-pattern-mask"></view><view class="corner-ornament corner-ornament-left corner-ornament--purple"></view><view class="corner-ornament corner-ornament-right corner-ornament--gold"></view><text class="eyebrow">只读小册页</text><text class="hero-title">出走小技能</text><text class="subtext">这些不是指令，只是一些可以复制走的小提醒。</text></view>
  <view class="floral-divider"><view class="floral-divider__line"></view><view class="floral-divider__dot purple"></view><view class="floral-divider__dot"></view><view class="floral-divider__line"></view></view><view wx:for="{{skills}}" wx:key="title" class="archive-card skill-card ornament-card--purple"><view class="corner-ornament corner-ornament-left corner-ornament--purple"></view><text class="tiny-seal">小技能</text><text class="section-title">{{item.title}}</text><text class="body-text">{{item.content}}</text><button class="sticker-button green" data-index="{{index}}" bindtap="copySkill">复制这条</button></view>
</view>
